{"surahDetails":{"id":96,"arabicName":"العلق","banglaName":"রক্তপিণ্ড","englishName":"The Clot","enTranslatedName":"Al-'Alaq","arLocation":"مكية","enLocation":"meccan","totalWords":72,"totalLetters":281,"audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio-surah/128/ar.alafasy/96.mp3","totalAyah":19},"surah":{"id":96,"verses":[{"id":1,"arabic_text":"ٱقۡرَأۡ بِٱسۡمِ رَبِّكَ ٱلَّذِي خَلَقَ","bangl_text":"পাঠ করুন আপনার পালনকর্তার নামে যিনি সৃষ্টি করেছেন","english_text":"Recite in the name of your Lord who created","page":597,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/6107.mp3","colorText":"ٱ<tajweed class=qalaqah>قْ</tajweed>رَأْ بِ<tajweed class=ham_wasl>ٱ</tajweed>سْمِ رَبِّكَ <tajweed class=ham_wasl>ٱ</tajweed>لَّذِى خَلَ<tajweed class=qalaqah>ق</tajweed>َ <span class=end>١</span>"},{"id":2,"arabic_text":"خَلَقَ ٱلۡإِنسَٰنَ مِنۡ عَلَقٍ","bangl_text":"সৃষ্টি করেছেন মানুষকে জমাট রক্ত থেকে।","english_text":"Created man from a clinging substance","page":597,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/6108.mp3","colorText":"خَلَقَ <tajweed class=ham_wasl>ٱ</tajweed>لْإِ<tajweed class=ikhafa>نس</tajweed>َ<tajweed class=madda_normal>ـٰ</tajweed>نَ مِنْ عَلَ<tajweed class=qalaqah>ق</tajweed>ٍ <span class=end>٢</span>"},{"id":3,"arabic_text":"ٱقۡرَأۡ وَرَبُّكَ ٱلۡأَكۡرَمُ","bangl_text":"পাঠ করুন, আপনার পালনকর্তা মহা দয়ালু","english_text":"Recite, and your Lord is the most Generous","page":597,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/6109.mp3","colorText":"ٱ<tajweed class=qalaqah>قْ</tajweed>رَأْ وَرَبُّكَ <tajweed class=ham_wasl>ٱ</tajweed>لْأَكْرَمُ <span class=end>٣</span>"},{"id":4,"arabic_text":"ٱلَّذِي عَلَّمَ بِٱلۡقَلَمِ","bangl_text":"যিনি কলমের সাহায্যে শিক্ষা দিয়েছেন","english_text":"Who taught by the pen","page":597,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/6110.mp3","colorText":"ٱلَّذِى عَلَّمَ بِ<tajweed class=ham_wasl>ٱ</tajweed>لْقَلَمِ <span class=end>٤</span>"},{"id":5,"arabic_text":"عَلَّمَ ٱلۡإِنسَٰنَ مَا لَمۡ يَعۡلَمۡ","bangl_text":"শিক্ষা দিয়েছেন মানুষকে যা সে জানত না।","english_text":"Taught man that which he knew not","page":597,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/6111.mp3","colorText":"عَلَّمَ <tajweed class=ham_wasl>ٱ</tajweed>لْإِ<tajweed class=ikhafa>نس</tajweed>َ<tajweed class=madda_normal>ـٰ</tajweed>نَ مَا لَمْ يَعْلَمْ <span class=end>٥</span>"},{"id":6,"arabic_text":"كَلَّآ إِنَّ ٱلۡإِنسَٰنَ لَيَطۡغَىٰٓ","bangl_text":"সত্যি সত্যি মানুষ সীমালংঘন করে","english_text":"No! [But] indeed, man transgresses","page":597,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/6112.mp3","colorText":"كَلّ<tajweed class=madda_obligatory>َآ</tajweed> إِ<tajweed class=ghunnah>نّ</tajweed>َ <tajweed class=ham_wasl>ٱ</tajweed>لْإِ<tajweed class=ikhafa>نس</tajweed>َ<tajweed class=madda_normal>ـٰ</tajweed>نَ لَيَ<tajweed class=qalaqah>طْ</tajweed>غَىٰٓ <span class=end>٦</span>"},{"id":7,"arabic_text":"أَن رَّءَاهُ ٱسۡتَغۡنَىٰٓ","bangl_text":"এ কারণে যে, সে নিজেকে অভাবমুক্ত মনে করে।","english_text":"Because he sees himself self-sufficient","page":597,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/6113.mp3","colorText":"أ<tajweed class=idgham_wo_ghunnah>َن ر</tajweed>َّءَاهُ <tajweed class=ham_wasl>ٱ</tajweed>سْتَغْنَىٰٓ <span class=end>٧</span>"},{"id":8,"arabic_text":"إِنَّ إِلَىٰ رَبِّكَ ٱلرُّجۡعَىٰٓ","bangl_text":"নিশ্চয় আপনার পালনকর্তার দিকেই প্রত্যাবর্তন হবে।","english_text":"Indeed, to your Lord is the return","page":597,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/6114.mp3","colorText":"إِ<tajweed class=ghunnah>نّ</tajweed>َ إِلَىٰ رَبِّكَ <tajweed class=ham_wasl>ٱ</tajweed><tajweed class=laam_shamsiyah>ل</tajweed>رُّ<tajweed class=qalaqah>جْ</tajweed>عَىٰٓ <span class=end>٨</span>"},{"id":9,"arabic_text":"أَرَءَيۡتَ ٱلَّذِي يَنۡهَىٰ","bangl_text":"আপনি কি তাকে দেখেছেন, যে নিষেধ করে","english_text":"Have you seen the one who forbids","page":597,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/6115.mp3","colorText":"أَرَءَيْتَ <tajweed class=ham_wasl>ٱ</tajweed>لَّذِى يَنْهَىٰ <span class=end>٩</span>"},{"id":10,"arabic_text":"عَبۡدًا إِذَا صَلَّىٰٓ","bangl_text":"এক বান্দাকে যখন সে নামায পড়ে","english_text":"A servant when he prays","page":597,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/6116.mp3","colorText":"عَ<tajweed class=qalaqah>بْ</tajweed>دًا إِذَا صَلَّىٰٓ <span class=end>١٠</span>"},{"id":11,"arabic_text":"أَرَءَيۡتَ إِن كَانَ عَلَى ٱلۡهُدَىٰٓ","bangl_text":"আপনি কি দেখেছেন যদি সে সৎপথে থাকে।","english_text":"Have you seen if he is upon guidance","page":597,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/6117.mp3","colorText":"أَرَءَيْتَ إِ<tajweed class=ikhafa>ن ك</tajweed>َانَ عَلَى <tajweed class=ham_wasl>ٱ</tajweed>لْهُدَىٰٓ <span class=end>١١</span>"},{"id":12,"arabic_text":"أَوۡ أَمَرَ بِٱلتَّقۡوَىٰٓ","bangl_text":"অথবা খোদাভীতি শিক্ষা দেয়।","english_text":"Or enjoins righteousness","page":597,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/6118.mp3","colorText":"أَوْ أَمَرَ بِ<tajweed class=ham_wasl>ٱ</tajweed><tajweed class=laam_shamsiyah>ل</tajweed>تَّ<tajweed class=qalaqah>قْ</tajweed>وَىٰٓ <span class=end>١٢</span>"},{"id":13,"arabic_text":"أَرَءَيۡتَ إِن كَذَّبَ وَتَوَلَّىٰٓ","bangl_text":"আপনি কি দেখেছেন, যদি সে মিথ্যারোপ করে ও মুখ ফিরিয়ে নেয়।","english_text":"Have you seen if he denies and turns away","page":597,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/6119.mp3","colorText":"أَرَءَيْتَ إِ<tajweed class=ikhafa>ن ك</tajweed>َذَّبَ وَتَوَلَّىٰٓ <span class=end>١٣</span>"},{"id":14,"arabic_text":"أَلَمۡ يَعۡلَم بِأَنَّ ٱللَّهَ يَرَىٰ","bangl_text":"সে কি জানে না যে, আল্লাহ দেখেন","english_text":"Does he not know that Allah sees","page":597,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/6120.mp3","colorText":"أَلَمْ يَعْل<tajweed class=ikhafa_shafawi>َم ب</tajweed>ِأَ<tajweed class=ghunnah>نّ</tajweed>َ <tajweed class=ham_wasl>ٱ</tajweed>للَّهَ يَرَىٰ <span class=end>١٤</span>"},{"id":15,"arabic_text":"كَلَّا لَئِن لَّمۡ يَنتَهِ لَنَسۡفَعَۢا بِٱلنَّاصِيَةِ","bangl_text":"কখনই নয়, যদি সে বিরত না হয়, তবে আমি মস্তকের সামনের কেশগুচ্ছ ধরে হেঁচড়াবই","english_text":"No! If he does not desist, We will surely drag him by the forelock","page":597,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/6121.mp3","colorText":"كَلَّا لَئ<tajweed class=idgham_wo_ghunnah>ِن ل</tajweed>َّمْ يَ<tajweed class=ikhafa>نت</tajweed>َهِ لَنَسْفَع<tajweed class=iqlab>َۢا ب</tajweed>ِ<tajweed class=ham_wasl>ٱ</tajweed><tajweed class=laam_shamsiyah>ل</tajweed><tajweed class=ghunnah>نّ</tajweed>َاصِيَةِ <span class=end>١٥</span>"},{"id":16,"arabic_text":"نَاصِيَةٖ كَٰذِبَةٍ خَاطِئَةٖ","bangl_text":"মিথ্যাচারী, পাপীর কেশগুচ্ছ।","english_text":"A lying, sinning forelock","page":597,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/6122.mp3","colorText":"نَاصِيَ<tajweed class=ikhafa>ةٍ ك</tajweed>َ<tajweed class=madda_normal>ـٰ</tajweed>ذِبَةٍ خَاطِئَةٍ <span class=end>١٦</span>"},{"id":17,"arabic_text":"فَلۡيَدۡعُ نَادِيَهُۥ","bangl_text":"অতএব, সে তার সভাসদদেরকে আহবান করুক।","english_text":"Then let him call his associates","page":597,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/6123.mp3","colorText":"فَلْيَ<tajweed class=qalaqah>دْ</tajweed>عُ نَادِيَهُۥ <span class=end>١٧</span>"},{"id":18,"arabic_text":"سَنَدۡعُ ٱلزَّبَانِيَةَ","bangl_text":"আমিও আহবান করব জাহান্নামের প্রহরীদেরকে","english_text":"We will call the angels of Hell","page":597,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/6124.mp3","colorText":"سَنَ<tajweed class=qalaqah>دْ</tajweed>عُ <tajweed class=ham_wasl>ٱ</tajweed><tajweed class=laam_shamsiyah>ل</tajweed>زَّبَانِيَةَ <span class=end>١٨</span>"},{"id":19,"arabic_text":"كَلَّا لَا تُطِعۡهُ وَٱسۡجُدۡۤ وَٱقۡتَرِب۩","bangl_text":"কখনই নয়, আপনি তার আনুগত্য করবেন না। আপনি সেজদা করুন ও আমার নৈকট্য অর্জন করুন।","english_text":"No! Do not obey him. But prostrate and draw near [to Allah]","page":597,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/6125.mp3","colorText":"كَلَّا لَا تُطِعْهُ وَ<tajweed class=ham_wasl>ٱ</tajweed>سْجُ<tajweed class=qalaqah>دْ</tajweed> وَ<tajweed class=ham_wasl>ٱ</tajweed><tajweed class=qalaqah>قْ</tajweed>تَرِ<tajweed class=qalaqah>ب</tajweed> ۩ <span class=end>١٩</span>"}]}}